    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In nomine domini nostri Iehsu Christi dei eterni, anno ab eius
                        nativitate millesimo centesimo septuagesimo quinto, octavo kalende octubris,
                        indictione nona. Manifesti sumus nos <persName><name ref="Mothico"
                                >Mothiconis</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Bernardus">Bernardi</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Galgerius">Gualgerius</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Iacobus">Iacobus</name></persName> germani filii suprascripti
                        Mothiconis et <persName><name ref="Flordipero">Floredepero</name></persName>
                        uxor suprascripti Gualgerii, (…) ubi interfuit notitia <persName><name
                                ref="Bello">Belloni</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Alfanus">Alfani</name></persName> germanorum meorum (…) insimul
                        per hanc cartulam vendimus et tradimus tibi <persName><name ref="Montanus"
                                >Montanino</name></persName>, rectori <orgName key="#Hospitals"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3206"><rs key="#Hospitals">hospitalis</rs> de
                                <placeName ref="#places/3207" key="#Hospitals"
                            >Altopasso</placeName></orgName> (…), videlicet petiam unam de terra
                        nostra que est in loco ubi dicitur Ad Arbium, que est cultra una, que tenet
                        unum caput in terra <persName><name ref="Tiniosus">Tiniosi</name></persName>
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Cecus">Cechi</name></persName>, alterum in
                        terra heredis quondam <persName><name ref="Grugnus"
                        >Grungi</name></persName>, latus unum tenet in <rs key="#Forests">bosco</rs>
                        de <placeName ref="#places/3229" key="#Forests">Silva Salese</placeName>,
                        alterum *** (…). <foreign>Prezzo</foreign>: lib. decem bonorum denariorum.
                        (…) <foreign>Pena</foreign>: in duplum (…) et insuper penam argenti optimi
                        lib. VI. (…) Actum in <rs key="#Castle">castro</rs> de <placeName
                            ref="#places/3211" key="#Castle">Vivinaria</placeName> prope <rs
                            key="#Churches">ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/3226">Sancti
                            Michaelis</orgName>. (…) <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Wilicio"
                                >Guilicio</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Lambertus"
                                >Lamberti</name></persName> et <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Baialardus">Baialardus</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Aldebrandus">Aldobrandini</name></persName> et
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Rodulfinus"
                            >Rodolfinus</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Bernardus"
                                >Bernardi</name></persName> rogati <rs key="#Witness">testes</rs>
                        interfuerunt. (S) <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Aldricus"
                                >Aldricus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> donni imperatoris post traditam complevi et
                        dedi. (…)</ab>
